<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Lunex — Payment Success</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
body{background:#050709;color:#e2e8f0;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:20px}
.card{background:#0f1318;border:1px solid #253047;border-radius:16px;padding:48px;max-width:480px;width:100%;text-align:center;box-shadow:0 40px 80px rgba(0,0,0,.5)}
.icon{font-size:56px;margin-bottom:20px}
h1{font-size:24px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:10px;letter-spacing:-.3px}
p{font-size:14px;color:#94a3b8;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:24px}
.btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:12px 28px;background:#4e8cff;color:#fff;border-radius:9px;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;transition:.15s}
.btn:hover{background:#2563eb}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="card">
  <div class="icon">⏳</div>
  <h1>Payment Received!</h1>
  <p>Your payment is being confirmed on the blockchain. You'll receive your API key via email once confirmed — this usually takes 1–10 minutes depending on the network.</p>
  <p>Already have your key? Log in below.</p>
  <a href="/" class="btn">Go to Dashboard →</a>
</div>
</body>
</html>
